#To boost the battery life

1.Add repo to install laptop-mode-tools:
	
	sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/unstable
	sudo apt-get update

2.Install laptop-mode-tools
	sudo apt-get install laptop-mode-tools

3.Run&Configure it
	sudo lmt-config-gui

Optional:

4.See working status:
	cat /proc/sys/vm/laptop_mode 

5.Edit this file to change properties such as setting it enable when it is on battery:
	/etc/laptop-mode/laptop-mode.conf
